# VibeMarketer вЂ” Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A native-ready macOS desktop app that wraps your **15 HABITAT marketing skills** in a premium, marketer-friendly UI. No terminal required.

**Tech stack:** Electron + React + Vite В· Vanilla CSS design system В· Claude API (BYOK)

