## Key Features

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **15 HABITAT Skills** | All bundled вЂ” Ideation, Building, Launch, Meta phases |
| **Dynamic Forms** | Each skill gets custom inputs auto-mapped from SKILL.md |
| **Founder Context** | Fill once in Settings в†’ auto-shared to every skill |
| **Claude API** | BYOK model вЂ” key stored locally, never leaves machine |
| **Output Panel** | Markdown rendering, copy-to-clipboard, export to .md |
| **Design System** | Dark theme, glassmorphism, phase color-coding, Inter font |

