## What Was Tested

- вњ… Dev server starts at `http://localhost:5173/`
- вњ… Welcome screen renders with sidebar showing all 15 skills
- вњ… Skills grouped correctly by phase (4 categories)
- вњ… Clicking a skill shows correct dynamic form inputs
- вњ… Settings page renders API key + Founder Context forms
- вњ… Phase badges and color-coding work per skill
- вњ… API key warning banner shows when no key configured

